com.google.template.soy.shared.internal

Class SharedRuntime

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.template.soy.shared.internal.SharedRuntime

  • public final class SharedRuntime
extends Object
    Runtime implementation of common expression operators to be shared between the jbcsrc and Tofu backends.
